title: Cisco security advisory (AV25-633)
description: On October 1, 2025, Cisco published security advisories to address vulnerabilities in the following products:
products: Cisco Cyber Vision Center  versions 5.1 and 5.2 and prior
Cisco Unified CM, Unified CM SME  versions 12.5, 14 and versions prior to 15SU3
solution: Review the references and apply the necessary updates.
